snippet.title: Tôtem - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Something strange has appeared on earth – multiple gigantic beings with unique languages... and you're the only one who can deter them. You are the translator.

Translate, converse with, and deter unidentified entities! 
Learn about them through how they speak and what they say using their unique inhuman languages.

Available now at Itch.io
https://shakles.itch.io/totem
